Classlio is an offline attendance tracking application provided as an ad-supported service. This Privacy Policy explains how information is handled when you use the app.

1. Information Collection and Use
User-Entered Data

All attendance data, class details, student names, and records entered into Classlio are stored locally on your device only.
We do not collect, transmit, sell, or have access to this data.

Third-Party Advertising

To support free usage, Classlio uses Google AdMob for displaying advertisements.

AdMob may automatically collect limited information such as:

Advertising ID

IP address

Device and usage information

This data is collected and processed by Google, not by the app developer, and is governed by Googleâ€™s Privacy Policy:
https://policies.google.com/privacy

