No Sale of Data: We do not sell, rent, or share personal data as defined by applicable privacy laws.

3. Childrenâ€™s Privacy

Classlio is not directed to children and is intended for use by educators and professionals.

The app may contain names of students entered by the user for attendance purposes. This information:

Remains stored locally on the device

